quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  42,23,"Ko ngon welo-welo mawngo, woni ko Allah wewlinirta jeyaaﾉ兎 Makko ﾉ兎n, e junngo Nulaaﾉ兎 Makko on; ﾉ兎n jeyaaﾉ兎 gomﾉ擁mﾉ兎 Allah e Nulaaﾉ兎 Makko ﾉ兎n, ﾉ兎 golli golle moﾆｴﾆｴe. An Nulaaﾉ熔, maaku: mi ﾉ預ﾉ橡妬raa on njoﾉ電i woo, e ko mi yottinta kon, si wanaa njoﾉ電i wootiri, ndi nafitorton onon; ndin woni: nde yiﾉ熔rton lam, fii ko mi enﾉ預m mon. Kala faggitiiﾉ熔 moﾆｴﾆｴere, Men ﾉ兎ydanay mo njoﾉ電i e hoore mayre: moﾆｴﾆｴere nden, ko sappo yeru mayre. Pellet, Allah ko Haforoowo junuubi kala tuubuﾉ熔 e jeyaaﾉ兎 Makko ﾉ兎n, mantoowo golle maﾉ橡兎 moﾆｴﾆｴe ﾉ容n ﾉ容 ﾉ兎 gollirta fii Makko."
  42,24,"Hini jeyaa e ko sirkooﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n aaﾆｴii, wonnde Muhammadu (yo o his) fefindi ndee Alqur'aanaare, o dammbi nde e Joomi makko. Allah ruttiiri ﾉ兎 wiide: hara a aru fefindaade fenaande woo, Ma Mi notu e ﾉ兎rnde maa nde, Mi meha meere fefindaande nden, Mi heddina goonga kan. Nde tawnoo non, wanaa non woniri, ﾉ蓉m tinndinii wonnde Annabiijo on (yo o his) ko wahayu Joomi makko o wonndi e mun. Pellet le, ko O Annduﾉ熔 ko woni e ﾉ兎rﾉ容 jeyaaﾉ兎 Makko ﾉ兎n. Huunde suuﾉ預aki Mo e mum."
  42,25,"Ko Kanko Allah woni jaﾉ登owo tuubuubuyee jeyaaﾉ兎 Makko yedduﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n, si ﾉ兎 ruttike e Makko, O yawtana ﾉ兎 bonﾉ擁 ﾉ擁 ﾉ兎 faggitii ﾉ擁n, e hoore Himo anndi kala ko huuwoton. Huunde suuﾉ預aki Mo e golle mon ﾉ容n. Ma O yoﾉ妬toy on ﾉ容."
  42,26,"Himo jaabina toraare gomﾉ擁mﾉ兎 Allah e Nulaaﾉ熔 Mun on, ﾉ兎 golli golle moﾆｴﾆｴe, O ﾉ兎ydana ﾉ兎 e ko ﾉ兎 lamndaaki mo kon, ka ﾉ砥ral Makko. Yedduﾉ兎 Allah e Nulaaﾉ熔 Mun ﾉ兎n non, hino woodani ﾉ兎 lepte saﾉ葉uﾉ容, habbitiiﾉ容 ﾉ兎 ﾃ疎lnde Darngal."
  42,27,"Si tawno Allah yaﾃｱﾃｱanno jeyaaﾉ兎 Makko ﾉ兎n fow arsike, ko pellet, ﾉ兎 bewirayno tooﾃｱe ka hoore leydi; kono Himo jippinira arsike on, emmbere ko O muuyi yaﾃｱﾃｱude O ﾉ妬llina. Pellet, ko O humpitiiﾉ熔 fii jeyaaﾉ兎 Makko ﾉ兎n, Reenuﾉ熔 ﾉ兎. O okkiray ﾃｱeﾃｱﾆｴal Makko ngal, O ﾉ妬llinira ngal kadi."
  42,28,"Ko Kanko woni jippinoowo ndiyam ﾉ預m e jeyaaﾉ兎 Makko ﾉ兎n, ﾉ殿awo ﾉ兎 taﾆｴaade fii majjam, O saaka ﾉ預m ndiyam, ﾉ預m fuﾉ擁na leydi ndin. Ko Kanko kadi woni Giﾉ熔 heftuﾉ熔 fii maﾉ橡兎, Yettiniiﾉ熔 e kala fiyaakyu."
  42,29,"Hino jeyaa e maandeeji tindinayﾉ擁 e kattal e gootaagu Makko ngun: tagugol kammuuli ﾉ擁n e leydi ndin, e ﾉ擁n ruugayﾉ擁 haawniiﾉ擁, ﾉ擁 O saakiti hakkunde majji. Kanko e fii mooﾉ妬ndiroygol ﾉ兎 ngol ﾃｱaawa ﾉ兎 yoﾉ妬ta ﾉ兎, nde O haaji e mun woo, ko O hattanﾉ熔. O ronkataa fii mun, wano woniri O ronkaano tagugol ﾉ兎 ka arannde laawol."
  42,30,"Kala ko heﾉ妬 on, onon ﾉ兎e yimﾉ兎, immorde e musiiba wonkiijii mon maa e jawle mon, ko sabu geddi ﾉ擁 juuﾉ容 mon ﾉ容n faggitii. Allah non, hino yaafoo ko ﾉ蓉uﾉ擁 e mun, hara O nanngitirtaa on ﾉ擁n."
  42,31,"On wonaa hattanﾉ兎 laawagol lepte Joomi ﾉ容n, si O faandanike on ﾉ容; On maraa kadi yawti Mo Kanko, woni giﾉ熔 hettoowo fii mon, wanaa ballo faabotooﾉ熔 on e lepte Makko ﾉ容n, si O faandanii mon ﾉ容."